								repellat voluptatem numquam fuga a reiciendis soluta hic illo!
								Omnis facilis reiciendis beatae culpa?"
							</p>
							<p class="opinions__content-item--data">Aplik, 28.03.2023r.</p>
						</div>
						<div class="opinions__content-item">
							<p class="opinions__content-item--value">
								"Lorem ipsum, dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit.
