							</p>
							<p class="opinions__content-item--data">Aplik, 28.03.2023r.</p>
						</div>
						<div class="opinions__content-item">
							<p class="opinions__content-item--value">
								"Lorem ipsum, dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit.
								Molestias nam adipisci fugit, quas, ad tenetur perspiciatis
								repellat voluptatem numquam fuga a reiciendis soluta hic illo!
								Omnis facilis reiciendis beatae culpa?"
							</p>
							<p class="opinions__content-item--data">Aplik, 28.03.2023r.</p>
						</div>

						<div class="opinions__content--arrow-previous">
							<svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"
								xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
								<path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd"
									d="M12 24L13.722 22.3283L4.5936 13.2L24 13.2L24 10.8L4.5936 10.8L13.6968 1.69688L12 1.04907e-06C7.6068 4.3932 4.2048 7.7952 -1.04907e-06 12L12 24Z"
									fill="url(#paint0_linear_346_4212)" />
								<defs>
									<linearGradient id="paint0_linear_346_4212" x1="12" y1="24" x2="12" y2="1.04907e-06"
										gradientUnits="userSpaceOnUse">
										<stop stop-color="#F6D4BA" />
										<stop offset="1" stop-color="#F6D4BA" stop-opacity="0.45" />
									</linearGradient>
								</defs>
							</svg>
						</div>
						<div class="opinions__content--arrow-next">
							<svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"
